videos.headline: Memphis ties it up on Taylor's TD run
videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. powers his way through two defenders to get into the end zone and score a Memphis touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis ties it up on Taylor’s TD run) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis' White throws 50-yard TD strike to Jones
videos.description: Brady White connects with Kedarian Jones, who barely gets one foot in the end zone to score on a 50-yard touchdown pass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis' White throws 50-yard TD strike to Jones) 2019/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cat runs onto the field at USF
videos.description: During the third quarter of Memphis' game with USF, a cat runs onto the field right before a Tigers kickoff, then scurries off the field and under a cart on the sideline.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cat runs onto the field at USF) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
